Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2015 17:40:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 06/25] x86/platform/intel/baytrail: Add comments about why we
 disabled HPET on Baytrail

commit b58d930750135d6c5b8e5aa084c0e9303c78c286 upstream.

This question has been asked many times, and finally I found the
official document which explains the problem of HPET on Baytrail,
that it will halt in deep idle states.

